{"tid":1598201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"若我們接受了政府的對話，我們已死去的朋友是不會原諒我們的","createTime":"2019-09-27T10:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T13:30:15.000Z","uid":133519,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"be198d4d19fdd87c43520e9e43cd646577b1cec5","tid":1598201,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mCekY6w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmCekY6w.png&h=6ef838e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">梁凌杰：<br />\n全面撤回送中。我們不是暴動。釋放學生傷者。林鄭下台。</span><br />\n<br />\n我哋仲去同林鄭對話？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">盧曉欣：<br />\n雖然抗爭時間久了，但絕對不能忘記，我們一直以來的理念。</span><br />\n<br />\n我哋仲去同林鄭對話？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">長沙灣麥烈士：<br />\n不是民選的政府是不會回應訴求，香港需要的是革命！</span><br />\n<br />\n而我哋高叫革命，卻走回頭路，去同林鄭對話？"},{"pid":"3053ae109143155104829bc203237d1bf8bb6286","tid":1598201,"uid":272976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63078a4a872aae21a424b8e2275f6f7812771986","tid":1598201,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:27:04.000Z","msg":"我們死去的朋友不會原諒和理傾"},{"pid":"18f1875e45d2f4d0156e97c250bdc8b7f7816aa2","tid":1598201,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91cc9f0095d754a9efaca2047489118ece716268","tid":1598201,"uid":98141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:34:37.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"d34fac85f37888b7b0e0b4a371b6a91d1503734c","tid":1598201,"uid":69946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:34:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c716122c63acb8a819e68507a1fc764393cb67f2","tid":1598201,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s